<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <h4>Node-MySql Login</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Inicio</a></li>
            <li><a href="/profile">Perfil</a></li>
            <li><a href="/auth/logout">Sair</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="avatar-ctn">
                        <img src='/img/SeekPng.com_avatar-png_1150053.png' class="avatar" alt="user profile picture" /></img>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">{{user.name}}</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Here’s a quick example to demonstrate Bootstrap’s form styles. Keep reading for documentation on required classes, form layout, and more.</p>
                        <a href="#" class='btn btn-primary'>{{user.email}}</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-8">
                <div class="card text-center">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        Pagina do Perfil
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Oi, {{user.name}} bem vindo de volta!</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Essa é a sua pagina de perfil onde pode adicionar todas as informações sobre você!</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Vai para algum lugar</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        Node MySql - Project
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>